OL,3,CBoy, 4, died at home after incident
OL,4,Cinvolving cast iron roller
OL,6,FA four-year-old boy died after a cast
OL,7,Firon roller went over part of his
OL,8,Fbody, an inquest has been told.
OL,10,FMaldwyn 'Gwern' Evans died in the
OL,11,Fgarden of his home in Tynreithin,
OL,12,FTregaron, on Thursday, 20 June.
OL,14,FAn inquest into his death opened at
OL,15,Fthe Aberystwyth Justice Centre on
OL,16,FWednesday, 26 June,
OL,18,FThe hearing was told that the boy was
OL,19,Finjured while pushing a vintage cast
OL,20,Firon roller, which went over part of
OL,21,Fhis body.
