OL,6,FSenior coroner Peter L Brunton said a
OL,7,Fpost-mortem examination had not
OL,8,Fconcluded, and adjourned the full
OL,9,Finquest to 9 October.
OL,11,FIn a statement released via Dyfed-
OL,12,FPowys Police, the boy's family said:
OL,13,F"As a family, we are incredibly
OL,14,Fdistraught by our tragic loss, and he
OL,15,Fwill be greatly missed by us and the
OL,16,Fentire community.
