OL,6,F"He was a loving son and a caring
OL,7,Fbrother, who touched the hearts of so
OL,8,Fmany. He lived his short life to the
OL,9,Ffullest and will be remembered for his
OL,10,Fcaptivating personality.
OL,12,F"He was an extremely keen little
OL,13,Ffarmer who had knowledge and ability
OL,14,Fbeyond his years.
OL,16,F"We would like to thank everyone for
OL,17,Ftheir support and kindness at this
OL,18,Fhorrific time. It has meant so much to
OL,19,Fthe whole family.
