OL,7,Fwould ask to be given privacy in which
OL,8,Fto do so."
OL,10,FIn a previous statement, the police
OL,11,Fforce said: "The death is not being
OL,12,Ftreated as suspicious and H.M Coroner
OL,13,Fhas been informed.
OL,15,F"Our thoughts are with the family who
OL,16,Fare receiving support and they have
OL,17,Fasked for privacy during this
OL,18,Fdifficult time."
